= About qubes-linux-dom0-updates =

qubes-linux-dom0-updates is a dom0 updater, after running the updates posting the
status on ''qubes/update-status''. The items are below

* Clone/Copy qubes-builder

* Assign the ''DIST_DOM0'' with the Qubes Repository Version.

* Attempt update

* Post update-status

